## [2026-01-29]
Version 0.99y

### Changed 
	* hyphens from hyphenation are now marked with an Artifact if tagging is active, and 
	no longer uses the U+00AD glyph by default, this resolves tagging issue #967.
	* active/softhyphen key has more options.
	* update parent-child rules for 2.0 (adapted to upcoming changes in ISO 32005 + best practice for math)
